152
00:10:17,060 --> 00:10:18,140
Call an ambulance.

153
00:10:19,890 --> 00:10:20,620
Are you okay?

154
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:23,540
Is it serious?

155
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:25,220
That car was too fast.

156
00:10:25,460 --> 00:10:26,940
Should we call an ambulance?

157
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:28,070
Where's the driver?

158
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:45,580
Xining.

159
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:46,980
Mr. Ji.

160
00:10:47,380 --> 00:10:48,710
I wasn't expecting you.

161
00:10:49,490 --> 00:10:50,750
We came to check on you.

162
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:52,700
I'm fine.

163
00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:54,820
Sorry.

164
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:56,820
For what?

165
00:10:57,460 --> 00:10:58,660
I was there too,

166
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:00,500
and I was the closest to Yu Le.

167
00:11:00,610 --> 00:11:01,610
I didn't save him.

168
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:03,380
Qi, it was not your fault.

169
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:04,960
It was an accident.

170
00:11:07,130 --> 00:11:07,580
No.

171
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:09,380
If I had saved him,

172
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:11,160
