187
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:47,420
Are you relieved now?

188
00:11:48,490 --> 00:11:49,620
What about Yu Le?

189
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:52,220
We'll see.

190
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:53,660
We…

191
00:11:57,140 --> 00:11:57,730
Xining.

192
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:00,440
