273
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:34,700
Yes.

274
00:15:35,340 --> 00:15:36,340
You won't regret it?

275
00:15:36,340 --> 00:15:38,060
I won't lie to myself.

276
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:39,870
I do feel it's a pity.

277
00:15:42,060 --> 00:15:42,390
Fine.

278
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:44,500
I respect your decision.

279
00:15:44,530 --> 00:15:45,660
Thank you, Yingjun.

280
00:15:45,940 --> 00:15:46,500
Get changed.

281
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:46,980
Okay.

282
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:57,660
You said you won't divorce me!

283
00:15:57,660 --> 00:15:58,540
